Attached is the final copy of the Court's jury questionnaire, which will be distributed by the Jury Department to 
prospective jurors beginning tomorrow. The final version incorporates the redline changes from Dkt. No. 365. 
Otherwise, a few minor non-substantive formatting changes were made to pages 1 and 5. 
Sincerely, 
Chambers of the Hon. Alison J. Nathan
